    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## eBook Summarizer Automation (TTS using Eleven labs)\n\nAdd the summarized text (English and Nepali) on the [Sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10GQLAP4CuBuXM2SvUBf7ULV4tVhhCXNQx4MBLivXg8s/edit?gid=801323258#gid=801323258), and change the Audio status to pending.\n\nExecute the Workflow! That's it!\n\nFlow:\nFetch Summarized text -> Switch passes it to Elevenlabs (IF Success )-> Upload the file to drive and change the status from pending the generated along with the generated audio link attached. \n(IF failed) -> Mark as failed and outputs the error message to the remarks column on sheets.\n\n## Attach Header and footer Audio sample across every generated audio #DONE",
        "height": 304,
        "width": 902
      },
